snippet.textDisplay:
THANKS Joe, we have been following along every day this is a great initative!

Would it be possible to get a shout out next Friday - 3rd April for my son's birthday as we didn't expect to spend his birthday in lockdown.

LEWIS fell off some monkey bars and broke his wrist 10min after schools closed last week so he was very excited to see you had a slpint just like his on the same arm. Lewis will be 7 on Friday 3rd and it would be a great start to the day to get a shout out during the work out !

Lewis, Rachel Mum & Dad in Glasgow.
